    "document_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"fr\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Générateur de Titres Automatiques | Votre Contenu, Nos Titres</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"Créez des titres percutants et optimisés pour le SEO, l\">\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Roboto+Condensed:wght@400;700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --color-primary: #8e22cc; /* Dark purple */\n            --color-secondary: #ffc107; /* Amber */\n            --color-text-light: #f8f9fa;\n            --color-text-dark: #343a40;\n            --color-background-dark: #212529;\n            --color-background-medium: #343a40;\n            --color-border: #495057;\n            --font-display: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            --font-ui: 'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: var(--font-ui);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: var(--color-text-light);\n            background-color: var(--color-background-dark);\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n            font-family: var(--font-display);\n            color: var(--color-text-light);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--color-background-dark);\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            color: var(--color-secondary);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            color: var(--color-text-light);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            background-color: var(--color-background-medium);\n            padding: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--color-secondary);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .form-group {\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--color-text-light);\n            font-family: var(--font-ui);\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n        }\n\n        input[type=\"text\"],\n        textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 0.8rem 1rem;\n            border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background-color: var(--color-background-dark);\n            color: var(--color-text-light);\n            font-family: var(--font-ui);\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        input[type=\"text\"]:focus,\n        textarea:focus {\n            border-color: var(--color-primary);\n            outline: none;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(142, 34, 204, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        textarea {\n            min-height: 120px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;\n            background-color: var(--color-primary);\n            color: var(--color-text-light);\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            font-family: var(--font-ui);\n        }\n\n        button:hover {\n            background-color: #a042e0; /* Lighter primary */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        button:active {\n            background-color: #7a1da0; /* Darker primary */\n            transform: translateY(0);\n        }\n\n        .result-section {\n            padding: 3rem;\n            background-color: var(--color-background-medium);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .result-group {\n            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .result-group h3 {\n            font-size: 1.6rem;\n            color: var(--color-secondary);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .result-item {\n            background-color: var(--color-background-dark);\n            border: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;\n            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            gap: 1rem;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .result-item span {\n            flex-grow: 1;\n        }\n\n        .copy-btn {\n            background-color: transparent;\n            color: var(--color-primary);\n            border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);\n            padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 0.85rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 0.5px;\n            flex-shrink: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .copy-btn:hover {\n            background-color: var(--color-primary);\n            color: var(--color-text-light);\n        }\n\n        .copy-btn svg {\n            width: 14px;\n            height: 14px;\n            fill: currentColor;\n        }\n\n        .seo-section {\n            padding: 3rem;\n            background-color: var(--color-background-dark);\n            color: var(--color-text-light);\n            border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .seo-section h2 {\n            color: var(--color-secondary);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);\n        }\n\n        .seo-section p {\n            max-width: 900px;\n            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem auto;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            line-height: 1.8;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .seo-links {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 1rem;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .seo-links a {\n            color: var(--color-secondary);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n            border: 1px solid var(--color-secondary);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        .seo-links a:hover {\n            background-color: var(--color-secondary);\n            color: var(--color-background-dark);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: var(--color-background-dark);\n            color: var(--color-border);\n            font-size: 0.85rem;\n            border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);\n        }\n    </style>\n    <meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\">\n    <link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://generateur-de-titres-automatiques-3.onrender.com\">\n    <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Générateur de Titres Automatiques\">\n    <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Créez des titres percutants et optimisés pour le SEO, l\">\n    <meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://generateur-de-titres-automatiques-3.onrender.com\">\n    <meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\": \"https://schema.org\", \"@type\": \"WebApplication\", \"name\": \"Générateur de Titres Automatiques\", \"description\": \"Créez des titres percutants et optimisés pour le SEO, l\", \"url\": \"https://generateur-de-titres-automatiques-3.onrender.com\", \"applicationCategory\": \"UtilityApplication\", \"operatingSystem\": \"Web Browser\"}</script>\n</head>\n<body data-site-slug=\"generateur-de-titres-automatiques-3\" data-runtime-mode=\"analysis_tool\">\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Générateur de Titres Automatiques</h1>\n            <p>Créez des titres percutants et optimisés pour le SEO, l'engagement et la conversion. Des titres accrocheurs en un instant, pour tous vos contenus.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Votre Contenu, Nos Titres</h2>\n            <form id=\"tool-form\">\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"keywords\">Mots-clés principaux (séparés par des virgules)</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"keywords\" placeholder=\"Ex: SEO, marketing digital, rédaction web\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"topic\">Décrivez brièvement le sujet de votre contenu</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"topic\" placeholder=\"Ex: Un article de blog sur les meilleures pratiques pour optimiser son site pour Google en 2024.\" required></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"form-group\">\n                    <label for=\"audience\">Audience cible (optionnel)</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"audience\" placeholder=\"Ex: Entrepreneurs, PME, débutants en SEO\">\n                </div>\n                <button type=\"submit\" id=\"tool-submit\">Générer les Titres</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"result-section\" id=\"tool-result\" style=\"display:none;\">\n            <h2 id=\"result-headline\">Vos Nouveaux Titres</h2>\n            <div class=\"result-group\">\n                <h3>Style SEO</h3>\n                <div id=\"seo-titles\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"result-group\">\n                <h3>Style Attractif (Clickbait)</h3>\n                <div id=\"clickbait-titles\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"result-group\">\n                <h3>Style Expert</h3>\n                <div id=\"expert-titles\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"result-group\">\n                <h3>Style Doux / Informatif</h3>\n                <div id=\"soft-titles\"></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"result-group\">\n                <h3>Style Commercial / Conversion</h3>\n                <div id=\"commercial-titles\"></div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <section class=\"seo-section\">\n        <h2>Boostez Votre Visibilité et Votre Engagement</h2>\n        <p>Dans l'univers numérique saturé d'aujourd'hui, un titre percutant est la clé pour capter l'attention et générer du trafic qualifié. Notre générateur de titres automatique